No. 1245,

Misc.

O’Brien v. Interstate Commerce Commission. Clement Theodore Cooper for petitioner. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, and Beatrice Rosenberg for respondent.

C. A. D. C. Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Douglas are of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
